pageProduct.name: Thompson's Kelp 1400mg 120 Tablets
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Supports healthy thyroid gland function and body metabolism

Thompson's One-A-Day Kelp provides a natural rich source of iodine; necessary for the production of thyroid hormons in a convenient daily dose. It may be used to: 
- Maintain iodine levels within the normal range in the body
- Enhance iodine levels in the body
- Support healthy thyroid gland function
- Maintain healthy thyroid hormones and assist their production
- Support body metabolism
- Maintain geenral health & wellbeing

Warnings

Vitamin and/or mineral supplements should not replace a balanced diet

Ingredients

Active Ingredients: Fucus vesiculosus (Kelp) ext. 280mg
derived from dry whole plant 1.4g (1400mg)
equiv to Iodine 280mcg

Directions

Adults - Takje one tablet daily (with food), or as professionally prescribed

RECYCLABLE INFORMATION

Remove cap and recycle glass

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
